{"id": 59398, "date": "2025-08-20T04:00:31", "date_gmt": "2025-08-20T11:00:31", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59398"}, "modified": "2026-05-13T16:57:52", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-13T23:57:52", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-20-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/20/kingdom-of-days-august-20-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 20"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><b>1973:\u00a0</b>Bruce and the E Street Band kick off a seven-night stand at Oliver&#8217;s in Boston.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"3719\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1973-0820/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1973-0820.jpg?fit=467%2C700&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"467,700\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1973-0820\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1973-0820.jpg?fit=467%2C700&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3719 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1973-0820.jpg?resize=467%2C700&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"467\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1973-0820.jpg?w=467&amp;ssl=1 467w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1973-0820.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce records &#8220;Dollhouse&#8221; with the E Street Band at The Power Station in New York City. It will remain in the vault for almost two decades.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HpF_i71cqVQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDHpF_i71cqVQ\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1981:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys play one of their most legendary, emotional and impassioned shows: a benefit for the Vietnam Veterans of America Foundation at the Sports Arena in Los Angeles, the first show of a six-night stand. Opening with &#8220;Who&#8217;ll Stop the Rain&#8221; (played here because of its actual content rather than its literal title), this show also features Bruce&#8217;s only known performance of &#8220;Ballad of Easy Rider&#8221; and a beautiful, emotional rendition of &#8220;The River.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/KYg_CB7AElA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLsxNBNx2akeXblEifwMxIN_rVQmHg3JDY\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20530\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-08-20a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?fit=1064%2C1643&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1064,1643\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-08-20a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?fit=663%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20530 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?resize=758%2C1170&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1170\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?w=1064&amp;ssl=1 1064w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?resize=194%2C300&amp;ssl=1 194w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?resize=663%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 663w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?resize=768%2C1186&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20a.png?resize=995%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 995w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20531\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-08-20b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?fit=1661%2C1070&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1661,1070\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-08-20b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?fit=758%2C489&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20531 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?resize=758%2C488&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"488\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?w=1661&amp;ssl=1 1661w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?resize=300%2C193&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?resize=1024%2C660&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?resize=768%2C495&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20b.png?resize=1536%2C989&amp;ssl=1 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20532\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1981-08-20c/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?fit=985%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"985,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1981-08-20c\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?fit=577%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20532 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?resize=758%2C1345&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1345\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?w=985&amp;ssl=1 985w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?resize=169%2C300&amp;ssl=1 169w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?resize=577%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 577w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?resize=768%2C1363&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1981-08-20c.png?resize=866%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 866w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Yet another of the all-time great shows performed on this date&#8211;this time across the country at the Meadowlands, where Bruce and the band wrap up their ten-night Born in the U.S.A. stand. Steve Van Zandt makes his triumphant return to the E Street Band stage for the tour premiere of &#8220;Two Hearts&#8221; and the live debut of a powerful &#8220;Drift Away.&#8221; The show is available as part of Bruce&#8217;s official archive series, where you can hear the strength of the bond between Bruce and Steve across the years. The Miami Horns also guest-star at this show, and the horn-fueled &#8220;Tenth Avenue Freeze-Out&#8221; will be released in the <em>Live 1975-85\u00a0</em>box set.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wh94fFrW9pI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EN-YMk9oi1g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDEN-YMk9oi1g\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Eic-jyO0hbs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/quVN35CdjTs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wwjzfLqmY64?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDwwjzfLqmY64\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/G5-yWPJynjo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9h8p8op0vgg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28717\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-08-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?fit=1292%2C2027&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1292,2027\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-08-20\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?fit=653%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28717 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?resize=758%2C1189&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1189\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?w=1292&amp;ssl=1 1292w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?resize=191%2C300&amp;ssl=1 191w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?resize=653%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 653w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?resize=768%2C1205&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1984-08-20.jpg?resize=979%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 979w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"54151\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/the_herald_news_1984_08_24_41/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Herald_News_1984_08_24_41.jpg?fit=%2C&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"[]\" data-image-title=\"The_Herald_News_1984_08_24_41\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Herald_News_1984_08_24_41.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-54151\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/The_Herald_News_1984_08_24_41.jpg?w=758&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>Bruce makes a guest appearance with Joe Grushecky and the Houserockers (the first of what will become a long series across many years) at Marz American Style in Long Branch, New Jersey, playing an eclectic set with the band that includes Bruce originals, Joe originals, and classic covers. John Eddie and Dion DiMucci join for the encores. Listen to the entire fun set below.</p>\n<div id=\"v-u8yCOevT-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/u8yCOevT?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\